ope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoratio=
n: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000;=
 border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> throw lots of new cl=
aims at Twitter</a> =E2=80=94=C2=A0about its alleged bad security practices=
