f reasons for getting out of) his deal. But it=E2=80=99s a mess. What if th=
e whistle-blower complaint is entirely true? What if you put the worst poss=
ible spin on it?=C2=A0What if Twitter=C2=A0<em>has=C2=A0</em>been doing a b=
unch of miscellaneous fraud? It=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/28964827.283552/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9=
