none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> won=E2=80=99t trust Tet=
her</a>, or won=E2=80=99t be able to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/28964827.283552/aHR0cHM6Ly9jcnlwdG8ubmV3cy9jaXJjbGUtYW5k=
