oin for dollar-ish things or dollar-ish things for Bitcoin. But because the=
re are different flavors of dollar in the crypto world, the liquidity is fr=
agmented.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
