 most stablecoin pairs is a good thing - liquidity doesn=E2=80=99t have to =
be split between multiple stablecoins, making market makers=E2=80=99 job ea=
sier and markets overall more liquid.=E2=80=9D And then if you are a market=
 maker and you get Binance-flavored dollars, you can pretty easily turn the=
m into Coinbase-flavored dollars (USDC) to trade on Coinbase, or various ot=
