 don=E2=80=99t have the expertise or time to call up the managers of your h=
undreds of investments and tell them how to grow their sales. But you can v=
ote against staggered boards at all of those companies. If you are big and =
diversified enough, you have to care about systemic factors =E2=80=94=C2=A0=
climate change, social unrest and, sure,=C2=A0governance best practices=C2=
=A0=E2=80=94=C2=A0rather than specifics.</li></ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px =
